trailingComments.value:
*
     * Generate the KKBOX authorization uri for user agreeing to authorize your application.
     *
     * @param {string} scope - ['user_profile', 'user_territory', 'user_account_status'] The scope of resource that developers ask KKBOX users to authorize.
     * @return {Promise}
     * @example auth.device.generateAuthorizationUri('user_profile user_territory user_account_status')
     * @see https://docs.kkbox.codes/docs/kkbox-oauth-20-device-code-api

*
     * Generate the QRCode image which redirect to KKBOX authorization uri for user agreeing to authorize your application.
     *
     * @param {string} scope - ['user_profile', 'user_territory', 'user_account_status'] The scope of resource that developers ask KKBOX users to authorize.
     * @param {number} [image_size = 500]
     * @param {number} [logo_size = 500]
     * @param {string} [response_type = 'image'] - ['image', 'json']
     * @return {Promise}
     * @example auth.device.generateQRCodeImage('user_profile user_territory user_account_status')
     * @see https://docs.kkbox.codes/docs/generate-qr-code-image
